GContainer* luau_parseXML_updates (  char *  contents,
GError **  err
) 
 

Given an Luau XML repository file in memory (ie., as a character string), read it in and parse it, returning the results (a list of updates) in a GContainer of type GCONT_LIST.

  • contents is a string representing a Luau XML repository file
  • err is a GError which will store any recoverable run-time errors
    Returns:
    a GContainer of type GCONT_LIST of updates.
